leadingComments.value:
*
 * Generates noise.
 *
 * @private
 * @param {Number} size - The linear texture size.
 * @param {Number} format - The texture format.
 * @param {Number} type - The texture type.
 * @return {TypedArray} The noise data.

*
	 * Constructs a new noise texture.
	 *
	 * The texture format can be either `LuminanceFormat`, `RedFormat`,
	 * `RGFormat` (requires WebGL 2), `RGBFormat` or `RGBAFormat`.
	 *
	 * @param {Number} width - The width.
	 * @param {Number} height - The height.
	 * @param {Number} [format=RedFormat] - The texture format.
	 * @param {Number} [type=UnsignedByteType] - The texture type.
